{"tid":1531073,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"13歲全英國最年輕的爸爸綠了","createTime":"2019-09-02T06:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T07:55:55.000Z","uid":42097,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"9acbb7c48e4e5bf2f4a4db721cbd4990365d29c7","tid":1531073,"uid":42097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:18:25.000Z","msg":"2009年，當時僅13歲的帕頓（Alfie Patten）宣布其15歲女友史蒂特蔓（Chantelle Steadman）懷孕了，被媒體封為「全英國最年輕的爸爸」，沒想到寶寶出世以後，DNA檢驗卻顯示孩子生父另有其人，令他情緒崩潰，陷入憂鬱。據外媒報導，10後的他現時是人生失敗者，無業又酗酒，還在緩刑當中，昨日因酒後鬧事被控刑事毀壞罪。<br />\n<br />\n23歲的帕頓被控刑事毀壞罪，昨日現身路易斯皇家法庭（Lewes Crown Court）。檢察官赫爾麗（Hannah Hurley）表示，他在街上跑來跑去，沿路亂砸車輛，胡亂生事，還咒罵一名年長居民，「他喝醉後四處咒罵，對著車子大吼大叫，非常具有攻擊性。」<br />\n<br />\n辯護律師法坦尼亞（Nutan Fatania）說，帕頓目前無業，與母親同住，他因酗酒問題困擾，已經和家庭醫生溝通減少酒量，「這名年輕人已經察覺到問題所在，他想要進步，恢復正常並且尋求平靜，而不是繼續從事危害健康，具有破壞性又混亂的行為。」<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ryhLfB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ryhLfB.jpg&h=aedfa030&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YYediAC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYYediAC.jpg&h=4109bece&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WRyUNtX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWRyUNtX.jpg&h=655bd005&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9738618ca0bf93fbf15b74f6c0d5088c6ca6d91","tid":1531073,"uid":22624,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:20:36.000Z","msg":"條女咁豬"},{"pid":"44d29713bccd0e7a06947d64bda54b247aa9cffb","tid":1531073,"uid":167509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"黎香港就重生既啦"},{"pid":"55146cdfb8a4a7bcbc3046f4f613ea2948f21e03","tid":1531073,"uid":109701,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"44d29713bccd0e7a06947d64bda54b247aa9cffb","tid":1531073,"uid":167509,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:23:12.000Z","msg":"黎香港就重生既啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T06:25:00.000Z","msg":"係咪可以同你老母大戰<img src=\"